title of '''Archdruid''' was bestowed upon certain powerful [[druid]]s that took on additional responsibilities within their given [[druidic circle]].

{{Quote|Even in death, each creature plays its part in maintaining the Great Balance. But now an imbalance grows, a force that seeks to hold sway over nature...we seek mainly to protect and educate, to preserve the Great Balance, but there are times when we must rise up against danger and
eradicate it.|The archdruid Safhran.}}
